    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. Mechanically, it runs smoothly with no major issues, and the service history is up to date. The exterior presents well, though you will find some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. It is a solid, dependable car that is ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
